snippet: Emory University officials say the FBI has joined an investigation into swastikas that were painted on the exterior of a historically Jewish fraternity house at the Georgia school....

headline.print_headline: FBI Investigating Swastikas at Ga. Frat House
headline.main: FBI Investigating Swastikas at Ga. Frat House

lead_paragraph: Emory University officials say the FBI has joined an investigation into swastikas that were painted on the exterior of a historically Jewish fraternity house at the Georgia school.
